message: "If you use this whitepaper in research, articles, or product design, please cite it as below. / 若您於研究、文章、產品設計中引用本書，請依以下格式。"
title: "Baiyuan GEO Platform: A Whitepaper on Building a SaaS for Generative Engine Optimization"
abstract: >-
  A technical whitepaper documenting the engineering practice of building
  Baiyuan GEO Platform (2024-2026), a SaaS system for Generative Engine
  Optimization. Covers a seven-dimension AI citation-rate scoring algorithm,
  AI-Bot-friendly shadow document delivery (AXP), Schema.org three-layer
  entity knowledge graph, closed-loop hallucination detection &
  auto-remediation, F12 three-layer structural optimizer (V1 rule-based +
  V3.1 dual-engine AutoGEO + E-GEO), rag-backend-v2 LLM hallucination
  hardening (six defense layers), platform SSOT chain (brand_faq /
  page_type / alerts), cross-border China GEO (Hong Kong edge node,
  UA routing, ICP-free central compliance, bidirectional AI visibility),
  AXP HTML Mirror-First (semantic HTML shadow docs mirroring customer
  origin), multimodal GEO (zero-touch ImageObject / VideoObject injection),
  and a five-layer cache-invalidation architecture for zero-touch
  propagation. Traditional Chinese and English complete (chapters 1-19,
  ~60,000 characters); Japanese complete (chapters 1-19).
